      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title II of the Social Security Act and the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to coordinate the threshold requirement for coverage of domestic employees under Social Security with the amount required for a quarter of coverage.</title>
